{"tha-ap430:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap430:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap430:0.3":"Sucintitattheraapadana ","tha-ap430:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap430:1.2":"ahosim kassako tada; ","tha-ap430:1.3":"Kasikammena jivami, ","tha-ap430:1.4":"tena posemi darake. ","tha-ap430:2.1":"Susampannam tada khettam, ","tha-ap430:2.2":"Dhannam me phalinam ahu; ","tha-ap430:2.3":"Pakakale ca sampatte, ","tha-ap430:2.4":"Evam cintesaham tada. ","tha-ap430:3.1":"Nacchannam nappatirupam, ","tha-ap430:3.2":"janantassa gunagunam; ","tha-ap430:3.3":"Yoham sanghe adatvana, ","tha-ap430:3.4":"aggam bhunjeyya ce tada. ","tha-ap430:4.1":"Ayam buddho asamasamo, ","tha-ap430:4.2":"dvattimsavaralakkhano; ","tha-ap430:4.3":"Tato pabhavito sangho, ","tha-ap430:4.4":"punnakkhetto anuttaro. ","tha-ap430:5.1":"Tattha dassamaham danam, ","tha-ap430:5.2":"navasassam pure pure; ","tha-ap430:5.3":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap430:5.4":"hattho pinitamanaso. ","tha-ap430:6.1":"Khettato dhannamahatva, ","tha-ap430:6.2":"sambuddham upasankamim; ","tha-ap430:6.3":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap430:6.4":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap430:6.5":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap430:6.6":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap430:7.1":"‘Navasassanca sampannam, ","tha-ap430:7.2":"ayagosi ca tvam mune; ","tha-ap430:7.3":"Anukampamupadaya, ","tha-ap430:7.4":"adhivasehi cakkhuma’. ","tha-ap430:8.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap430:8.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap430:8.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap430:8.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap430:9.1":"‘Cattaro ca patipanna, ","tha-ap430:9.2":"cattaro ca phale thita; ","tha-ap430:9.3":"Esa sangho ujubhuto, ","tha-ap430:9.4":"pannasilasamahito; ","tha-ap430:9.5":"Yajantanam manussanam, ","tha-ap430:9.6":"punnapekkhana paninam. ","tha-ap430:10.1":"Karotopadhikam punnam, ","tha-ap430:10.2":"sanghe dinnam mahapphalam; ","tha-ap430:10.3":"Tasmim sangheva databbam, ","tha-ap430:10.4":"tava sassam tathetaram. ","tha-ap430:11.1":"Sanghato uddisitvana, ","tha-ap430:11.2":"bhikkhu netvana sangharam; ","tha-ap430:11.3":"Patiyattam ghare santam, ","tha-ap430:11.4":"bhikkhusanghassa dehi tvam’. ","tha-ap430:12.1":"Sanghato uddisitvana, ","tha-ap430:12.2":"bhikkhu netvana sangharam; ","tha-ap430:12.3":"Yam ghare patiyattam me, ","tha-ap430:12.4":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham. ","tha-ap430:13.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap430:13.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap430:13.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap430:13.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap430:14.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","tha-ap430:14.2":"sovannam sappabhassaram; ","tha-ap430:14.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","tha-ap430:14.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","tha-ap430:15.1":"Ekunavisatimam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap430:16.1":"Akinnam bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap430:16.2":"nariganasamakulam; ","tha-ap430:16.3":"Tattha bhutva pivitva ca, ","tha-ap430:16.4":"vasami tidase aham. ","tha-ap430:17.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap430:17.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap430:17.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap430:17.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap430:17.5":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap430:17.6":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap430:18.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap430:18.2":"labhami amitam dhanam; ","tha-ap430:18.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap430:18.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:19.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap430:19.2":"sivikam sandamanikam; ","tha-ap430:19.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap430:19.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:20.1":"Navavattham navaphalam, ","tha-ap430:20.2":"navaggarasabhojanam; ","tha-ap430:20.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap430:20.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:21.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","tha-ap430:21.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","tha-ap430:21.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap430:21.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:22.1":"Dasiganam dasaganam, ","tha-ap430:22.2":"nariyo ca alankata; ","tha-ap430:22.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap430:22.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:23.1":"Na mam sitam va unham va, ","tha-ap430:23.2":"parilaho na vijjati; ","tha-ap430:23.3":"Atho cetasikam dukkham, ","tha-ap430:23.4":"hadaye me na vijjati. ","tha-ap430:24.1":"Idam khada idam bhunja, ","tha-ap430:24.2":"imamhi sayane saya; ","tha-ap430:24.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap430:24.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:25.1":"Ayam pacchimako dani, ","tha-ap430:25.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap430:25.3":"Ajjapi deyyadhammo me, ","tha-ap430:25.4":"phalam tosesi sabbada. ","tha-ap430:26.1":"Navasassam daditvana, ","tha-ap430:26.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap430:26.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap430:26.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap430:27.1":"Vannava yasava homi, ","tha-ap430:27.2":"mahabhogo anitiko; ","tha-ap430:27.3":"Mahapakkho sada homi, ","tha-ap430:27.4":"abhejjapariso sada. ","tha-ap430:28.1":"Sabbe mam apacayanti, ","tha-ap430:28.2":"ye keci pathavissita; ","tha-ap430:28.3":"Deyyadhamma ca ye keci, ","tha-ap430:28.4":"pure pure labhamaham. ","tha-ap430:29.1":"Bhikkhusanghassa va majjhe, ","tha-ap430:29.2":"buddhasetthassa sammukha; ","tha-ap430:29.3":"Sabbepi samatikkamma, ","tha-ap430:29.4":"denti mameva dayaka. ","tha-ap430:30.1":"Pathamam navasassanhi, ","tha-ap430:30.2":"datva sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap430:30.3":"Imanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap430:30.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:31.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap430:31.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap430:31.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap430:31.4":"navasassassidam phalam. ","tha-ap430:32.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap430:32.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap430:32.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap430:33.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap430:33.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap430:33.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap430:34.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap430:34.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap430:34.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap430:35.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sucintito thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap430:36.1":"Sucintitattherassapadanam atthamam. "}